### Notes API Test Requests
### Base URL: https://empty-x3pd.onrender.com

### Variables
@baseUrl = https://empty-production-a85c.up.railway.app
#@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Get all notes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notes

### 2. Create a new note
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notes
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "My First Note",
  "content": "This is the content of my first note"
}

### 3. Get a specific note (replace 1 with actual ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notes/1

### 4. Update a note (replace 1 with actual ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/notes/2
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Updated Title",
  "content": "Updated content here"
}

### 5. Delete a note (replace 1 with actual ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/notes/1

### 6. Create another note for testing
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notes
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Test Note",
  "content": "This is a test note"
}

### 7. Create a note with only title (content is optional)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notes
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Note without content"
}

### 8. Create a second note

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notes
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "My second Note",
  "content": "This is the content of my second note"
}